ğŸµ Streams:
Ayer: {streams_ayer}, Hoy: {streams_hoy} ({'ğŸ“ˆ' if dif_streams > 0 else 'ğŸ”»' if dif_streams < 0 else 'â–'} {dif_streams:+})

ğŸ‘¥ Listeners:
